This building forms part of the Icon Industrial Estate, a private 30Ha* industrial estate providing tenants with flexible leasing alternatives and expansion potential.

- 12m* truss height

-Optional hardstand to 10,000sqm* (with flood lighting)
- Wide roller shutter openings
- Drive around access

Outstanding opportunity to purchase a free standing quality built industrial factory in a prime location.

The factory has a truss height of 13 metres* and capacity to install gantry overhead cranes.

Direct truck access allows for excellent truck movements for loading and unloading.

This building forms part of the Icon Industrial Estate, a private 30 hectare industrial estate providing occupiers with flexible leasing alternatives.

This modern engineering workshop and office facility offers the industrial market high quality improvements and large external yard and lay down areas. There is the option to expand the site to the east, south and north.

Key attributes:

- Modern improvements
- High truss workshop
- Very high power capacity
- 32 tonne and 12.5 tonne gantry cranes
- Partitioned offices, good staff amenities including lunch room, showers and first aid room
- Direct access to freeway via new Mundijong Road extension

CBRE are pleased to present to the market this well designed industrial transport facility incorporating excellent infrastructure and frontage to Mandurah Road. Situated 35km* south of the Perth CBD within a high profile industrial estate amongst excellent quality industrial buildings.

The property will provide broad appeal to transport and associated industrial users requiring a combination of good quality office, workshop, hardstand, washdown and refuelling facilities. Bowsers and above ground diesel storage tanks are also available.

- OFFICE 344SQM*
- LUNCHROOM & AMENITIES 189SQM*
- WORKSHOP 1,363SQM*
- WORKSHOP OFFICE 75SQM*
- STORAGE SHED 177SQM*
- WASHDOWN BAY BUILDING 238SQM*

CBRE and JLL 4,000sqm* - 9,000sqm* of office/factory space with various overhead cranes situated on 40,500sqm* of land.

The truss height of the factories is 12 metres* with large openings for access.

A power supply of 1,600 amps* is available.

The property is available for lease on flexible lease terms. Make an offer.
